returnValues.name: isActive
returnValues.description: Indicates whether the screen wake lock is currently active and the screen is prevented from sleeping.

returnValues.name: isSupported
returnValues.description: Indicates if the Screen Wake Lock API is available in the current browser/device.

returnValues.name: release
returnValues.description: An asynchronous function to manually release the wake lock and allow the screen to sleep again.

returnValues.name: request
returnValues.description: An asynchronous function to request a new screen wake lock.
